name: LMTD EDITION #WARRIOR Thizzler Tee
description:
Support the movement, steez out your wardrobe & rep your favorite NBA team & #BayArea website all at the same time!

The first Thizzler merch since 2011, the #WARRIOR tee is a new angle on the traditional Thizzler logo. And with the Warriors colorway, you can show love to the Bay's favorite basketball team while repping the official home for Bay Area music!

This is a LMTD EDITION piece. This piece is only available until December 1st, 2013. Even in the event that we decide to bring this design back in the future, it will never have the LMTD EDITION text ever again, so they'll always know who copped it first!

10.0 oz 100% Cotton Tubular Jersey. Classic fit, double-needle bottom hem and sleeves with shoulder-to-shoulder tape. Pre-shrunk to minimize shrinkage.

All orders will ship on December 9th, and the first 25 orders will come with Thizzler stickers!

Design: Walter Cruz
Concept: Erica Haikara

name: HM5 Autographed Hard Copy

name: Limited Edition Hustla Movement 1-5 Bullet USB
description: A limited edition Bullet USB drive with all 5 Hustla Movement mixtapes pre-loaded onto it. Listen to Young Gully's progression from HM1 to HM5, without having to change CDs.
